content: Very easy to use! Couldn't ask for a better sidekick on my floods!
Works awesomely, use it daily.

Great app.  I have been doing water damage restoration for 15 years and I use it multiple times  a day on every water loss that I go to.   It is perfect for the initial equipment calculations and daily monitoring reports.   Everything on this app is absolutely flawless.    Keep growing and expanding the capabilites of this outstanding app!!!

This app is hands down the most superior app in its class. Finally an affordable electronic version of most of the paperwork and notes we carry around for reference. Eliminates a lot of tedious calculations. It isn't a full scale restoration program, but it has the potential to be.  Besides, it allows for a lot more freedom than those other appsAnd as an added bonus, A GLOSSARY! I've been in the water restoration industry for over a decade and everything in the app is very up-to-date and on point. Great job
I give five stars, but would like to see some direct dry units added on the power category and in some of the calculation categorys. Like the e tes units. Thanks for a great app.
